{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_05_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 幽霊より怖いんです！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "白い着物の女の人が……\n本物の幽霊が、こっちにどんどん近づいて来る……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A woman in a white kimono…\nA real ghost is getting closer and closer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3785794061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、早く檻に入るんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ get into the cage quickly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（いいぞ、そのまま幽霊を怖がってくれ）\n（そうすればドッキリ企画は大成功だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Good‚ keep getting scared of the ghost…)\n(If you do that‚ the prank plan will be a huge success.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7197970301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "檻に閉じ込められて逃げ場がない私に\n幽霊が迫って来るなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trapped in this cage with nowhere to run…\nAnd a ghost is approaching me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8014868498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "まるでホラー映画のワンシーンみたいです！\nなんだかワクワクしてきました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like a scene from a horror movie!\nI'm starting to feel excited!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7929122727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうくるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as I thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "幽霊さん、初めまして\n私はサニーピースの白石千紗です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ Mrs.Ghost.\nI'm Chisa Shiraishi from Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースって分かりますか？\nアイドルグループの名前なんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you know Sunny Peace?\nIt's an idol group…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（幽霊相手に急に自己紹介し始めたぞ！？）\n（一体どうするつもりだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She's introducing herself to a ghost!?!)\n(What on earth is she planning?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルはみんなを笑顔にするのがお仕事なので\n幽霊さんも笑顔になってもらえたら嬉しいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols have the job of making everyone smile‚\nSo I'd be happy if even a ghost could smile because of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、笑顔は難しい感じですか？\nそうですよね、幽霊ですもんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ is it difficult for a ghost to smile?\nI guess so‚ you're a ghost after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたら幽霊さんは笑ってくれるのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what I can do to make the ghost smile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（幽霊でも笑顔にしたいなんて、さすがアイドルだな）\n（そこまでして幽霊と打ち解けたいのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Trying to make a ghost smile… Truly an idol's spirit.)\n(She's really trying to get close to the ghost‚ huh?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　いつもファンのみんなは\n私と握手すると笑顔になってくれるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got it! Fans always smile when they shake hands with me‚\nEven a ghost like you might smile",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "幽霊さんも、私と握手しませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "if you shake hands with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そ、そうですよね、握手なんてしたくないですよね\n調子に乗ってごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ w-well‚ of course‚ you wouldn't want to shake hands‚ right?\nSorry for getting carried away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（落ち込む千紗を見て幽霊が焦ってるぞ）\n（罪悪感に駆られたのか、おずおずと手を出して……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Seeing Chisa feeling down‚ the ghost seems to be getting anxious.)\n(Seems like it's feeling guilty‚ hesitantly reaching out its hand…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……。ありがとうございます\nふふ、幽霊さんと握手会しちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Thank you very much.\nHehe‚ I just had a handshake event with a ghost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（幽霊に襲われてるのに、なんだこの和やかな雰囲気は）\n（このドッキリはお蔵入り決定だな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Despite being attacked by a ghost‚ what's with this friendly atmosphere?)\n(This prank is definitely going into the vault…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3733.33333330001,
          "startTime": 130.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（ん？　メッセージが……こ、これは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Huh? A message… Th-this is…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗、ちょっといいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Chisa‚ can I talk to you for a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "はい、なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ what is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "たった今、スタッフから終了の連絡が来たんだ\nどうやら諦めたらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just now‚ we received a message from the staff that the prank is over.\nIt seems they've given up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "なんの話ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗、このプラカードを見てくれ\nてってれー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Chisa‚ take a look at this sign.\nTa-da!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……ドッキリ大成功……\n……ええええええええ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… The prank was a huge success…\n…Wha…whaaaaat?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "今日一番の悲鳴だな\nもっと早くその声を聞きたかったよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The loudest scream of the day.\nI wish I heard that voice sooner…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
